+      "url": "https://example.com/reference?topic=openwiki",
+      "capturedAt": "2026-07-18T12:00:00.000Z",
+      "title": "Optional title",
+      "context": "Optional reason this was saved",
+      "source": "Optional provenance label"
+    }
+  ]
+}
+```
+
+`url` and `capturedAt` are required. Do not add private, signed, or
+credential-bearing URLs. Run `openwiki ingest links --print`, or rely on
+`openwiki ingest all` and the existing all-source schedule. The connector
+preserves the original URL, removes fragments and common tracking parameters
+from its canonical URL, derives a stable source ID, and writes only new or
+changed records to `~/.openwiki/connectors/links/raw/<runId>/links.json`.
+Repeated unchanged runs write no raw manifest and skip synthesis.
